n, May og Hammond gjorde til sitt varemerke. S\u00e5 gjenst\u00e5r det da \u00e5 se om LeBlanc klarer \u00e5 konkurrere med sine forgjengere hva seertall gjelder."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "264dfc31bf4772612bb90e096d61124461b08a0808afa81776ffac0db56d3e78"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-09-27T06:21:08.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Friends-stjernen f\u00e5r n\u00f8klene til BBCs kongerike for to sesonger"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13542351.ece/p9fhhj/ALTERNATES/w980-default/matt.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/c8600ef5d7bdf90caa427f286e56ba431b98fe01.jpg?595fb536"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Matt LeBlanc tar over Top Gear -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "c8600ef5d7bdf90caa427f286e56ba431b98fe01"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Top Gear", "tv", "bil"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Top Gear,tv,bil"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["sesong", "forrige sesong"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["news", "twitter", "the grand tour", "studios", "top gear", "may og hammond", "amazon prime", "richard hammond og jeremy clarkson"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "england"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["mark linsey", "richard hammond", "matt leblanc", "james may", "jeremy clarkson", "chris evans"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13542351.ece/p9fhhj/ALTERNATES/w980-default/matt.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-sit